'''偉彭醫療'''（Anthem, Inc.）是美国的一家[[醫療保險|醫療保險]]公司，偉彭醫療在[[财富美国500强|财富美国500强]]中排名第29位<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fortune 500 Companies 2020: Who Made the List|url=https://fortune.com/fortune500/2020/search/|publisher=[[财富_(杂志)|财富 (杂志)]]|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206111637/https://www.forbes.com/pictures/eddk45gjikm/exxonmobil/}}</ref>。2004年，总部位于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的WellPoint，Inc和总部位于[[印第安納波利斯|印第安納波利斯]]的偉彭（Anthem）合并為現今的偉彭醫療<ref name="changes">{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/wellpoint-changes-its-name-to-anthem-1407877202|title=WellPoint Changes Its Name to Anthem|author=Matthews|first=Anna Wilde|work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date=August 12, 2014|accessdate=2021-03-26|archive-date=2018-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221200802/https://www.wsj.com/articles/wellpoint-changes-its-name-to-anthem-1407877202}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Health Insurer WellPoint Switches Name to Anthem|url=https://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/sdut-health-insurer-wellpoint-switches-name-to-anthem-2014dec03-story.html|date=December 3, 2014|publisher={{link-en|San Diego Union Tribune}}|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2019-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190805131001/https://www.sandiegouniontribune.com/sdut-health-insurer-wellpoint-switches-name-to-anthem-2014dec03-story.html}}</ref>。截至2018年，该公司拥有约4000万会员<ref name=10K/>。

